data.description: The perfect combination of country charm and city convenience located on 3 lovely fenced acres.  You will immediately feel at home as you step inside surrounded by the warm and inviting knotty pine paneling and walls/ceiling.  Master is conveniently located on the main level.  Two additional bedrooms are located upstairs, one with built in desks and space for two beds or a large sized guest suite with a bathroom conveniently located between the bedrooms. There is a den off the kitchen area adding even more living space.  Easy access to the garage through the breezeway to get to the car or shop on chilly days.  In additon to the charming home, this property also includes a five-stall barm complete with a tack room, providing ample space for housing horses or other livestock.  The property is fully fenced and gated.  With water and electricity readily available to the barn, caring for your animals is made easy and convenient.  Whether you are an avid equestrian or simply appreciate the rustic charm of a barn, this unique opportunity is yours to explore and make your own!
